open the microwave collect the knife from microwave
slice the potato with the knife inside the microwave and close
turn around from microwave and turn towards the microwave
open the microwave place the knife inside the microwave and close
turn left and turn right towards the microwave
open the microwave collect the sliced potato from microwave and close
turn right move forward turn right move forward towards the sink bring down the sliced potato
place the sliced potato inside the sink rinse with water and collect the sliced potato

high_descs: Turn back and walk towards the microwave oven
Open the oven and take a knife out of the oven
Cut the potato into pieces which is kept inside the oven and close the oven
Take a 360 degree turn and stand in front of the oven
Open the oven and put the knife inside it and close the oven
Move little bit towards the left side of the oven

Turn towards back and reach the sink
Put the potato piece in the sink, clean it with water and take it off

high_descs: Turn around and go to the microwave on your right.
Open the microwave and pick up the knife inside it.
Cut the potato inside the microwave and close it.
Turn right, then turn right again in the direction of the countertop and then turn around in the direction of the microwave.
Put the knife inside the microwave.
Turn left and then turn to the microwave to your right.
Take out a slice of the potato from the microwave.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the slice of the potato inside the sink, rinse it and then pick it up.
Go to the fridge to your left.
Put the potato inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Putting a clean slice of potato inside the fridge.
